caption:
Liquid love....
Flowing through my veins...
Liquid love...

("Liquid Love" - Madonna, Unreleased 1999)

Having my morning shake and it is truly like liquid love, flowing through my veins.  Herbalife is more than a shake, more than the number one nutrition company in the world, it is a way of LIFE!  It is constantly learning and developing the mind and the body!

When you feel so good in your own skin and know you're treating your body right and giving it what it needs to get you to reach your goals, what other people think means nothing!  I love myself more, I love my family and friends more, I love LIFE.  So drinking my shake this morning is like drinking liquid LOVE!

#BestLifeEver
#HerbaHero
